title: Onion Pretzel Snacks
ingredients: ["1 pkg. Snyders sourdough pretzels", "1/2 lb. butter (not margarine)", "1 envelope Lipton onion soup mix"]
directions: ["Break pretzels into bite size pieces.", "Place in a 9 x 13-inch pan.", "Melt butter and add onion soup mix.", "Stir well.", "Pour over pretzels and mix well.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for 15 minutes, stirring every 5 minutes.", "Let cool completely.", "Store in tightly closed container."]

title: Mock Lemon Pie
ingredients: ["2 c. water", "1 1/2 c. sugar", "5 heaping Tbsp. flour", "salt", "1 tsp. vinegar", "2 egg yolks", "1 tsp. lemon extract", "2 egg whites", "2 Tbsp. sugar"]
directions: ["Mix and cook together the first 5 ingredients.", "Add eggs and lemon extract; cook a little bit more.", "Cool and pour into baked pie crust.", "Beat egg whites; add 2 tablespoons sugar.", "Put on top and brown in hot oven."]
